226
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,480
Ursinho.

227
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:33,960
E agora, obviamente,
um espertinho também.

228
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,040
Toque.

229
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:46,040
Miau.

230
